Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Welcome to this unique opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Imagine your dream home right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.42,0:00:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}A rare, permit-issued building lot awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Picture a stunning modern design coming to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.84,0:00:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}This lot measures twenty-five by one hundred twenty-five feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Envision the possibilities for your vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Severance is already approved, how exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The city has assigned a unique address.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}A building permit is in hand, ready for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Investors and builders will see great potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Create a masterpiece that stands out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}This is more than just land; it&apos;s a canvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}A chance to craft a contemporary haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Picture yourself in a vibrant new community.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The possibilities are endless on this lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Imagine the joy of designing your own space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Thank you for exploring this opportunity with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}I can&apos;t wait to see your vision unfold.
